description: Available at: https://openstudionetwork.com/keezer - Highlights from Geoffrey's stunning re-imagining of the Rush classic "Limelight", from his latest solo album Heart of the Piano (2013 - Motéma). Geoffrey discusses Hank Jones' influence on his harmonic conception, and takes you step-by-step through his arpeggiated right hand triplet patterns in dialogue with the left hand.  Includes a PDF of the complete note-for-note transcription from the recording. (Level: Advanced)
